data.description: GORGEOUS HOME NESTLED IN DESIRABLE LAKE CAROLINA COMMUNITY, ZONED FOR AWARD-WINNING RICHLAND 2 SCHOOLS! This 3 bedroom/ 2.5 bath home is full of amazing features! Natural light spills throughout the flowing layout as you move with ease from one room to the next. The large living room features a cozy fireplace, hardwood floors, and easy access to the kitchen! The spacious and bright eat-in kitchen boasts ample counter and cabinet space making cooking a breeze! The owner's suite offers a walk-in closet and spa-like en suite with a soaking tub! Each additional bedroom features ample closet space and access to a lovely shared full bath. Enjoy relaxing or entertaining with family and friends in the stunning sun room or on the large deck that looks out onto the fully-fenced backyard! Also take in all Lake Carolina has to offer with shopping, community pool and community dock!
